Hector Autoscale module
================

Extension to hector, for autoscaling of a Cassandra cluster.

Currently a master thesis work done by Andreas Baakind at University of Oslo (toraba at ifi dot uio dot no).



HOWTO
===============
1. Goto https://github.com/hector-client/hector and download hector-client sourcecode
2. Download autoscale sourcode, and copy to hector/autoscale
2. open pom.xml, and append autoscale as a module
3. Build hector-client from master-pom



CONFIG
==============
Parameters may be changed from src/main/resources/autoscale.yaml